{"Id":555251,"Title":"读书乐","Dynasty":"明","Author":"李贽","Context":"天生龙湖，以待卓吾。天生卓吾，乃在龙湖。龙湖卓吾，其乐何如。四时读书，不知其余。读书伊何，会我者多。一与心会，自笑自歌。歌吟不已，继以呼呵。恸哭呼呵，涕泗滂沱。歌匪无因，书中有人。我观其人，实获我心。哭匪无因，空潭无人。未见其人，实劳我心。弃置莫读，束之高屋。怡性养神，辍歌送哭。何必读书，然后为乐。乍闻此言，若悯不谷。束书不观，吾何以欢。怡性养神，正在此间。世界何窄，方册何宽。千圣万贤，与公何冤。有身无家，有首无发。死者是身，朽者是骨。此独不朽，愿与偕殁。倚啸丛中，声震林鹘。歌哭相从，其乐无穷。寸阴可惜，曷敢从容。","PoertyType":null,"Cipai":"","Status":1,"Rank":0,"Tag":null,"Explanation":null,"First":null,"Guid":"ddd15a86b49359d7aafec85e52fcd2e4","Step":0,"Verses":[{"Id":6459458,"Sentence":"有身无家，有首无发。","Rank":0,"PoetryId":null,"Pinyin":"yǒu shēn mó gū ，yǒu shǒu mó fā ","Tag":null,"Explanation":null,"English":null,"Sort":20,"Dynasty":"明"},{"Id":6459459,"Sentence":"死者是身，朽者是骨。","Rank":0,"PoetryId":null,"Pinyin":"si zhě shì shēn ，xiu zhě shì gū ","Tag":null,"Explanation":null,"English":null,"Sort":21,"Dynasty":"明"},{"Id":6459438,"Sentence":"天生龙湖，以待卓吾。","Rank":0,"PoetryId":null,"Pinyin":"tiān shēng lóng hú ，yi dāi zhuó wú ","Tag":null,"Explanation":null,"English":null,"Sort":0,"Dynasty":"明"},{"Id":6459439,"Sentence":"天生卓吾，乃在龙湖。","Rank":0,"PoetryId":null,"Pinyin":"tiān shēng zhuó wú ，nǎi zài lóng hú ","Tag":null,"Explanation":null,"English":null,"Sort":1,"Dynasty":"明"},{"Id":6459440,"Sentence":"龙湖卓吾，其乐何如。","Rank":0,"PoetryId":null,"Pinyin":"lóng hú zhuó wú ，jī lè hé rú ","Tag":null,"Explanation":null,"English":null,"Sort":2,"Dynasty":"明"},{"Id":6459441,"Sentence":"四时读书，不知其余。","Rank":0,"PoetryId":null,"Pinyin":"sì shǐ dòu shū ，bú zhī jī yú ","Tag":null,"Explanation":null,"English":null,"Sort":3,"Dynasty":"明"},{"Id":6459442,"Sentence":"读书伊何，会我者多。","Rank":0,"PoetryId":null,"Pinyin":"dòu shū yī hé ，huì wǒ zhě duō ","Tag":null,"Explanation":null,"English":null,"Sort":4,"Dynasty":"明"},{"Id":6459443,"Sentence":"一与心会，自笑自歌。","Rank":0,"PoetryId":null,"Pinyin":"yī yú xīn huì ，zì xiào zì gē ","Tag":null,"Explanation":null,"English":null,"Sort":5,"Dynasty":"明"},{"Id":6459444,"Sentence":"歌吟不已，继以呼呵。","Rank":0,"PoetryId":null,"Pinyin":"gē yǐn bú yi ，jì yi hū ā ","Tag":null,"Ex